response.original_title: Venables on Venables: The Terry Venables Story
response.overview: Terry Venables, from Dagenham to coaching triumphs like winning the Spanish league and leading England in Euro 96, is celebrated in this autobiographical film. A football icon, Venables' career, from playing for England to managing with tactical brilliance, is highlighted. The documentary captures his impact on the game until his passing in 2023.
response.title: Venables on Venables: The Terry Venables Story
